column3: There's nothing left to build now! Surely they could spare a paltry few minutes to come and collect these blasted things...
Complete 100 stellar missions in Sinus Ardorum to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
Good day to you, <hex:022C0DFF07><hex:022903EB0203><hex:FF02> <hex:0203>! Will you come and speak with me when you have a moment?
The Cosmic Exploration Initiative has barely taken its first steps. To truly blossom, it needs both your talents and your time!
<hex:022C0DFF07><hex:022903EB0203><hex:FF02> <hex:0203>! I'm so glad to see you. Will you come and speak with me when you have a moment?
I worry that other crew members may be in need of help but are too hesitant to ask for it. Might you keep an ear out for me?
Councilor Y'adebh's inspection couldn't have gone better. If I find another task in need of a measured approach, I shall be sure to come to you.
Complete 50 stellar missions on Phaenna to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
Ugh, it pains me to think of the tasks left unfinished back at the Hub... Is there <hex:021A020203>anyone<hex:021A020103> who might have a free moment?
To undertake a new quest from Mumukko, you will need to complete her quests in Sinus Ardorum.
